Author: Christian Grail
Message:
Add SAP Build Prototyping tool

SAP Build is a complete set of cloud‚Äëbased tools to design and build your enterprise app.
- Create clickable mockups of your application from your sketches. Then turn them into refined prototypes and bring them to life by dragging and dropping real SAP UI5 elements.
- Understand your users‚Äô needs. Collect informal feedback or easily create remote usability studies on each iteration of your design. SAP Build makes it easy to bring users into the design process.

A video of the product is available here: https://vimeo.com/182832619

https://www.build.me/

Author: Vladimir Berezovsky
Message:
Preparation for landing page To add new design tool topic: - enter new line - type
(make sure the id is as same as link to the topic in table of content) - leave the next line blank - write content you desire - leave next line empty again - type
in the next file to end topic take any
as an example. FAQs - What is
? + The content that won't be visible on the landing page. Include everything inside this tag and it will only be visible in markdown file. - What about
? + This is a container for navigation. There's no need to modify html tag. You can add new links to topics with no problems. - Can I write new tags? + Yes. Please be sure that there's some purpose for it. You can add your custom html tags as same as an article example on top. For any questions please contact me. Peace!
